tall poppy
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:someone who stands out above others
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: aka taller poppy; OED online:  b. Allusively, spec. as tall poppy: in Australia, an especially well-paid, privileged, or distinguished person; also transf.
